result.name: Hee Wan Roasted Kitchen

reviews.text: An experience to be remembered. Worth the effort. Menu with pictures so easy enough. Give it a go. Very good basic no frills dining.
The staff is friendly and attentive. Good food and nice interior.

Adjust to local cost of living, I think this is a great value consider its price, location and decoration.

Server were nice and quick. The place is newly renovated.

Would come again.

Worst food I had in HK, rice was old and sticky, char siu/pork bbq was cold and even after they microwaved, it was disgusting, amazing the ly are in business in high Street. Maybe either they discriminate foreigners, or the locals don't care.
The bbq pork is to die for. I have never tasted such delicious bbq pork in my life. Prices are reasonable. Service is fast. Love the food.

result.adr_address: 香港旺角砵蘭街187號號
result.name: 囍運燒臘餐廳小㕑

reviews.text:
最近リノベーションをして、かなり清潔なレストランに生まれ変わり、かなり人気店ともなっている鶏ローストをメインにした食堂。いわゆる香港のB級グルメ(茶餐庁と呼ばれる)の代表的な店舗だが、通りに面したガラス越しにこれ見よがしに鶏のローストがぶら下がっているのが見える。

メニューは鶏のローストを乗せたご飯はもちろんの事ながら、多種のおかず、野菜ロースト、炒め物、等が用意されており、単なるB級グルメでない事を感じさせられる。

お薦めは5種盛ご飯。鶏だけでなく中華ソーセージ、叉焼等一気に楽しむことが出来る。量はかなり多い。

混んでいる時は相席(香港デフォルト)も有るので。
上檯時，才通知 無瀨粉。
Food so so only, price slightly high. Rush and crowded environment.
又是以燒味食品主打，跟一般歺廳差不多。
It will be perfect if the system cn put zero star. Worst service ever. Dirty. Yuck
